  schema:name "Write a Basic Transaction in Ledger" ;
  schema:description "A Ledger transaction consists of a date, a payee/description, and two or more [postings](../terms/posting.md). The format is whitespace-sensitive — postings must be indented (by at least one space or tab; two spaces is conventional)." ;
